column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra,p.dec,p.petror9#_r, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, s.z as z_spec, s.zErr, zns.nvote, zns.p_el as elliptical, zns.p_cw as spiralclock, zns.p_acw as spiralanticlock, zns.p_edge as edgeon, zns.p_dk as dontknow, zns.p_mg as merger   FROM Galaxy as p    JOIN ZooNoSpec AS zns ON p.objid = zns.objid    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE (p.ra between # and #) and (p.dec between # and #) and (p.dered_g-p.dered_r)>#
